{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-compound-selectors/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-class/","description":"selector-max-combinators 限制一个选择器中组合选择器的数量 此规则在计算组合选择器的数量之前先解析选择器嵌套。选择器列表中的每个选择器都将单独计算。 选项 int：允许的最大组合选择器数量。 例如，使用 2： 以下模式被视为违规： 以下模式不被视为违规：","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"selector-max-combinators\"><a href=\"#selector-max-combinators\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>selector-max-combinators</h1>\n<p>限制一个选择器中组合选择器的数量</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> > <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">b</span> + <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">c</span> ~ <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">d</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">e</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/** ↑   ↑   ↑  ↑\n * 这些是组合选择器 */</span></code></pre>\n<p>此规则在计算组合选择器的数量之前先解析选择器嵌套。<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/selectors4/#selector-list\">选择器列表</a>中的每个选择器都将单独计算。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>int</code>：允许的最大组合选择器数量。</p>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>2</code>：</p>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">b</span> ~ <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">c</span> + <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">d</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">b</span> ~ <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">c</span> {\n  &#x26; > d {}\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">b</span> {\n  &#x26; ~ c {\n    &#x26; + d {}\n  }\n}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">b</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">b</span> ~ <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">c</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">b</span> {\n  &#x26; ~ c {}\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 选择器列表中的每个选择器都将单独计算 */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">b</span>,\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">c</span> > <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">d</span> {}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/selector-max-combinators.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-combinators/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-combinators/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-combinators/index.html.5a9b8182ad9ce05bc7b140f8d615bfd3.json"}